{"tid":1963123,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"仆街 世界末日架啦！！！！！武漢正式解封 無症狀帶病毒蝗正式打到黎！！！","createTime":"2020-04-08T02:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T03:59:18.000Z","uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"62e1b2c3916d06be76ba516b448d4eb424dc50dc","tid":1963123,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/charles984681/status/1247710520435773440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharles984681%2Fstatus%2F1247710520435773440&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=9c06fbe3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharles984681%2Fstatus%2F1247710520435773440&h=e9d7ce9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/charles984681/status/1247710520435773440</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/charles984681/status/1247593948580679680\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharles984681%2Fstatus%2F1247593948580679680&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBZtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=7bb4343f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcharles984681%2Fstatus%2F1247593948580679680&h=a1716827\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/charles984681/status/1247593948580679680</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀，佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「無症狀帶武漢病毒蝗殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生；無症狀帶武漢病毒蝗殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲「鳴呀，點解係我」就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切，有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到變左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。<br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" clas